 The “Ayo” singer took to her Instagram page to share pictures of her performance at the German Embassy in Nigeria. While delivering an electrifying perfomance she began sweating which later ruined her make up. An Instagram user upon seeing the post reacted saying  “Your makeup artist suppose get sack letter.” Simi, however, responded in a warm-hearted manner  “lol you idiot. Person no dey sweat for stage again?”   #Simi laughs off the “idiocy” of a follower A post shared by  Instablog9ja (@instablog9ja) on Oct 14, 2019 at 8:51am PDT //www.instagram.com/embed.js The post Simi Slams Internet Troll For Telling Her To Sack Her Make Up Artist appeared first on tooXclusive. Source: Too Xclusive